About The Role
Join ENGIE’s Supply & Energy Management team as a Trading Quantitative Analyst and help shape the mathematical models that support trading decisions across Australia and New Zealand’s energy markets.
In this role, you’ll work closely with analytics, trading, pricing and risk specialists to build, test and refine quantitative models that support commercial decision\u2011making. You’ll be part of a collaborative environment that values learning, innovation and diverse thinking.
Technical Excellence
Develop quantitative models to value OTC and electricity option contracts, applying advanced mathematical and statistical techniques.
Work alongside Forward Trading and Origination teams to refine models, ensuring they reflect market behaviour and support business strategies.
