Conduct comprehensive training sessions for clients, partners and colleagues to ensure effective use of the product. 
Develop training materials and documentation tailored to different user skill levels. 
Develop a deep understanding of Velixo and the ERP systems that we integrate with. Stay up to date with the latest industry trends in reporting techniques. 

