What you will do as the Assistant Director, Data

Working in the Technical and International team, you will be a leading data expert for the AER. You will use your specialist data skills, to contribute to a range of different matters including in support of investigations, monitoring, surveillance and economic regulatory functions. This will often involve working in multidisciplinary teams alongside line area team members and other specialists from the Technical and International team.

