 A demonstrated ability to manage, develop and mentor junior team members. Experience managing other data specialists is highly desirable. 
 Expertise in a broad range of data acquisition, processing, analysis and visualisation techniques and a demonstrated commitment to maintaining currency of that expertise. 
 Expertise in a broad range of data acquisition, processing, statistical, AI and machine learning techniques, including the ability to review the use of these techniques by others and a demonstrated commitment to maintaining currency of that expertise. 

