We are seeking an Energy Market Analyst – Market Modelling & Forecasting to join our Energy Markets Analytics team supporting trading and market analysis across the Australian National Electricity Market (NEM).
The primary focus of this role is NEM market modelling, including building and maintaining market models, developing assumptions and running scenarios to analyse future market dynamics.
